description: This file is a test fixture JavaScript module that imports a worker from another module and sets up message passing logic between a worker and the parent window. It also contains a conditional message posting outside the worker context.

methods.name: addEventListener
methods.description: Adds an event listener to the worker object for message events.

methods.name: postMessage
methods.description: Posts a message to the parent window or, if in worker context, posts a message back to the main thread.
